content:
Runs relevant Playwright end-to-end tests when test files or application pages are modified. Helps catch UI regressions early in the development process.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.spec.ts ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.spec.js ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *e2e*.ts ]]; then echo 'üé≠ Running Playwright tests...' && npx playwright test \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" --reporter=list && echo '‚úÖ E2E tests passed' || echo '‚ùå E2E tests failed'; elif [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *pages/*.tsx ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *app/*.tsx ]]; then PAGE_NAME=$(basename \"${CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH%.*}\"); echo 'üé≠ Running related E2E tests...' && npx playwright test --grep \"$PAGE_NAME\" --reporter=list 2>/dev/null || echo '‚ÑπÔ∏è No specific tests found for this page'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
